title: Jimmy Reed - I'm Jimmy Reed (1958) + Just Jimmy Reed (1962) (199
description:
Two original Vee-Jay albums of Jimmy Reed on one CD

Jimmy Reed's very first album I'm Jimmy Reed - a collection of previous Vee-Jay single releases and Jimmy's fourth album for Vee-Jay records, Just Jimmy Reed


Listening to these songs it's easy to understand why Jimmy's guitar & harp play  is regarded as very influental for generations of following blues & rock artists
